the physical electron charge

00:46:52.933 --> 00:46:53.975 align:middle line:90%
and then the bare charge.

00:46:53.975 --> 00:46:59.770 align:middle line:90%


00:46:59.770 --> 00:47:04.550 align:middle line:84%
So this is important for
the following reason.

00:47:04.550 --> 00:47:13.590 align:middle line:84%
So now you observe because
