covariant derivative does not

00:47:48.560 --> 00:47:49.060 align:middle line:90%
change.

00:47:49.060 --> 00:48:05.310 align:middle line:90%


00:48:05.310 --> 00:48:09.830 align:middle line:84%
So remember, the structure
of this covariant derivative

00:48:09.830 --> 00:48:13.400 align:middle line:84%
is needed for the
gauge invariance.

00:48:13.400 --> 00:48:17.150 align:middle line:84%
It's needed for the
