01:21:14.580 --> 01:21:20.430 align:middle line:84%
for making this
journey very enjoyable

01:21:20.430 --> 01:21:24.900 align:middle line:84%
and rewarding for myself, and I
hope you have learned something

01:21:24.900 --> 01:21:31.770 align:middle line:84%
from this class, and whatever
